docs {
  # Top Customers by Revenue
  
  Get top customers ranked by total sales (Customer Lifetime Value).
  
  ## Industry Metrics:
  - Total Sales (Revenue)
  - Total Orders
  - Average Order Value
  - Customer Lifetime Days
  - Last Order Date
  - Customer Segment
  
  ## Query Parameters:
  - `limit` (optional): Number of customers to return (default: 10)
  - `startDate` (optional): Filter from date
  - `endDate` (optional): Filter until date
}
